window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Charles Darklin thought finding relics would be the hard part. Turns out, surviving them is worse.</p> <p>After barely escaping the Vault of Morvaen, Charles and his team of fierce, beautiful women are on the Isle of Agua in search of the next artifact—the Totem of Tides. But this relic isn’t just guarded by traps or monsters. It’s alive.</p> <p>Haunted by visions of power, tyranny, and ruin, Charles is forced to confront the truth about himself—and the terrifying potential of the magic he wields. As the Rifts spread and the Weave frays, the line between salvation and destruction grows thinner by the day.</p> <p>With ancient mages whispering in his mind and his team’s loyalty pulling at his heart, Charles must decide whether to protect the people he loves… or the world that’s already falling apart.</p> <p>Because power always demands a price—and this time, the cost may be everything.</p>"; 
